1
00:00:14,302 --> 00:00:16,843
Zhimei, happy birthday!

2
00:00:17,763 --> 00:00:18,763
And your umbrella.

3
00:00:25,202 --> 00:00:26,202
Why hasn't she come yet?

4
00:00:27,702 --> 00:00:29,522
It's about to rain,

5
00:00:29,662 --> 00:00:32,403
just in time to give her back the umbrella.

6
00:00:36,443 --> 00:00:38,723
Zhimei, it's about to rain, let's go.

7
00:00:40,162 --> 00:00:41,422
It hasn't started raining yet.

8
00:00:42,463 --> 00:00:43,043
Move away from me.

9
00:00:43,043 --> 00:00:43,723
It's fine.

10
00:00:43,922 --> 00:00:44,863
Just in case.

11
00:01:06,162 --> 00:01:06,742
Alright.

12
00:01:08,003 --> 00:01:09,263
Good thing I didn't give it back.

13
00:01:51,163 --> 00:01:52,763
Happy birthday.

14
00:02:17,002 --> 00:02:17,662
What's wrong?

15
00:02:18,562 --> 00:02:19,342
Were you scared by the thunder?

16
00:02:21,002 --> 00:02:21,882
Make a wish.

17
00:02:27,243 --> 00:02:27,803
Wu Xi,

18
00:02:28,583 --> 00:02:29,623
I think

19
00:02:31,442 --> 00:02:32,542
we should talk.

20
00:02:32,542 --> 00:02:33,083
Zhimei,

21
00:02:41,502 --> 00:02:42,222
you know,

22
00:02:42,782 --> 00:02:44,502
the only thing that kept me going

23
00:02:45,782 --> 00:02:47,562
during the days I was locked up

24
00:02:50,002 --> 00:02:50,963
was the thought of seeing you.

25
00:02:53,542 --> 00:02:54,863
I swore to myself

26
00:02:55,382 --> 00:02:57,882
that I would see you no matter what.

27
00:02:59,463 --> 00:03:00,963
Now my wish has come true.

28
00:03:12,602 --> 00:03:13,123
Zhi Mei,

29
00:03:13,803 --> 00:03:14,863
I really

30
00:03:17,423 --> 00:03:18,423
love you.

31
00:04:11,322 --> 00:04:12,083
Happy birthday.

32
00:04:19,363 --> 00:04:20,623
I'm sorry.

33
00:04:22,062 --> 00:04:23,662
To keep you by my side,

34
00:04:24,743 --> 00:04:26,663
I want to be selfish again.

35
00:04:36,783 --> 00:04:39,562
Stop bothering me. It's over.

36
00:04:57,923 --> 00:04:58,803
You're awake.

37
00:05:06,082 --> 00:05:09,483
I'm too tired to fall asleep.

38
00:05:10,502 --> 00:05:12,723
I made you breakfast. I'll go get it.

39
00:05:12,942 --> 00:05:13,522
Thank you.

40
00:05:14,803 --> 00:05:15,902
Ye Zhimei!

41
00:05:16,262 --> 00:05:18,163
How can you still be sleeping at this time?

42
00:05:18,423 --> 00:05:20,322
The online public opinion is going wild.

43
00:05:21,642 --> 00:05:22,522
Ye Zhimei!

44
00:05:23,522 --> 00:05:24,402
Meimei.

45
00:05:35,043 --> 00:05:36,822
We've located the IP address of the other party

46
00:05:36,822 --> 00:05:38,623
through the flow of funds in the account.

47
00:05:38,623 --> 00:05:40,683
The IP is in this city,

48
00:05:40,743 --> 00:05:42,002
but it keeps changing.

49
00:05:43,142 --> 00:05:44,322
Keep tracking the IP address.

50
00:05:44,623 --> 00:05:45,163
Yes, sir.

51
00:05:48,642 --> 00:05:50,562
Sir, something big happened.

52
00:06:00,442 --> 00:06:02,683
Mr. Ye, it's not that we don't support you.

53
00:06:02,962 --> 00:06:04,522
But the public opinion is against you.

54
00:06:04,522 --> 00:06:06,123
The stock price dropped sharply.

55
00:06:06,642 --> 00:06:08,623
You must give up the management rights

56
00:06:08,623 --> 00:06:09,502
and stay out of the public eye.

57
00:06:10,043 --> 00:06:12,142
It's for the good of our group.

58
00:06:12,142 --> 00:06:13,462
I didn't do anything wrong.

59
00:06:13,663 --> 00:06:15,762
Retreat now is to admit guilt.

60
00:06:16,983 --> 00:06:18,623
Chenghai is my father's legacy.

61
00:06:18,822 --> 00:06:20,423
I won't give up my responsibility

62
00:06:20,642 --> 00:06:22,603
and position because of the rumors.

63
00:06:28,502 --> 00:06:29,223
Don't worry.

64
00:06:30,822 --> 00:06:32,623
We can hold a press conference together

65
00:06:32,623 --> 00:06:33,783
to clarify all the rumors.

66
00:06:33,783 --> 00:06:35,402
As long as we stand together,

67
00:06:35,402 --> 00:06:36,623
it's the best response.

68
00:06:37,163 --> 00:06:39,882
I agree. Now is the critical time to dispel rumors.

69
00:06:39,882 --> 00:06:42,502
You two facing it together as a couple

70
00:06:42,502 --> 00:06:44,183
is the most direct and effective way.

71
00:06:44,382 --> 00:06:46,882
If you wait any longer, you'll be completely passive.

72
00:07:14,262 --> 00:07:15,623
Here comes Mr. Ye.

73
00:07:15,822 --> 00:07:17,382
Mr. Ye,

74
00:07:17,382 --> 00:07:18,783
regarding the rumors of murder and infidelity,

75
00:07:18,783 --> 00:07:19,962
do you have any explanation?

76
00:07:19,962 --> 00:07:21,022
Nonsense.

77
00:07:21,502 --> 00:07:22,623
Our relationship has never changed

78
00:07:22,623 --> 00:07:23,663
due to any turmoil.

79
00:07:23,923 --> 00:07:25,062
Thank you all for your concern.

80
00:07:25,962 --> 00:07:27,962
Please do not spread false information

81
00:07:27,983 --> 00:07:29,522
to harm my wife.

82
00:07:30,343 --> 00:07:31,902
Today, I stand here

83
00:07:31,902 --> 00:07:33,462
not just to clarify rumors,

84
00:07:34,103 --> 00:07:35,462
but to announce something.

85
00:07:36,502 --> 00:07:37,402
Three months ago,

86
00:07:38,283 --> 00:07:40,082
the diving accident that caused my husband's disappearance

87
00:07:40,082 --> 00:07:41,243
was not an accident,

88
00:07:43,202 --> 00:07:44,123
but a conspiracy.

89
00:07:44,603 --> 00:07:45,663
Conspiracy?

90
00:07:46,762 --> 00:07:48,942
What? A conspiracy?

91
00:07:52,022 --> 00:07:52,822
From now on,

92
00:07:53,502 --> 00:07:55,502
I will offer a reward of millions of yuan in my name

93
00:07:55,843 --> 00:07:57,502
to collect clues and track down the real culprit.

94
00:07:58,243 --> 00:07:59,343
No matter who you are,

95
00:07:59,723 --> 00:08:00,683
or where you hide,

96
00:08:01,522 --> 00:08:02,202
I swear

97
00:08:03,043 --> 00:08:04,062
I will find you

98
00:08:04,642 --> 00:08:05,723
and bring you to justice.

99
00:08:07,283 --> 00:08:08,082
Watch out.

100
00:08:19,702 --> 00:08:20,502
Are you okay?

101
00:08:28,462 --> 00:08:29,223
Zhimei.

102
00:08:38,262 --> 00:08:39,603
Is this related to the case?
